    "content": "\n<section class=\"xmteditor\" style=\"display:none;\" data-tools=\"新媒体管家\" data-label=\"powered by xmt.cn\"></section><p style=\"line-height: 23.2727px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我参与  |  我体验  |  我快乐</span><br></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\"> </span><img class=\"__bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.45454545454545453\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015100ZpMrFj.jpg\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"22\" width=\"22\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015100JRozuN.jpg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 28px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">▲玻璃桥景区石牛寨：全透明高空玻璃桥，被誉为世界建筑奇迹</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 23.2727px; white-space: normal;\"><br></p>\n<p></p>\n<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86266\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86266\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(240, 0, 0); font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">惠  说  新  闻</strong></span></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><blockquote class=\"\" data-author=\"Wxeditor\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 20px; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">HUI  WEEK  NEWS</span></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: -0.3em auto 40px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 57, 31); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2017.7.24 星期一</span></p></section></section></section></blockquote></section></section></section></section></section></section><p></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 23.2727px; white-space: normal;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(15, 1, 1); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广度丨态度丨温度  </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0em; margin-left: 0em; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&lt; 古有世说新语，今有惠说新闻 &gt;</span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p></p>\n<article class=\"yead_editor\" data-author=\"Wxeditor\"><section><section class=\"yead_bdc\"><section><section><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015100Hl9LY1.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.16361416361416362\" data-w=\"819\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p></section></section></section></section></article><p></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1、全国首例电商平台打假案宣判：淘宝胜诉获赔12万元。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（16年5月，淘宝发现姚某销售的品牌猫粮存在假货嫌疑，经过猫粮品牌方的鉴定，该猫粮为掺假的品牌猫粮。）</span></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015100X8HcF9.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5417789757412399\" data-w=\"1113\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2、美“福特号”航母服役，系美军最大核动力航母。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（福特”号今年4月才开始海试，3个月后就急着宣布服役，这样的“带病服役”，在世界海军史上是相当罕见和不正常的。）</span></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015101cvoysS.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6527272727272727\" data-w=\"550\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3、现实版“一字千金”，中国文字博物馆悬赏认字。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（ 破译1个字奖10万。）</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015101it9s5j.jpg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.7078125\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4、青岛“空中列车”试运行，载500人最高时速可达70公里。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（国内最高速的悬挂式单轨列车。）</span></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/201707270151014Cbomc.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49584199584199584\" data-w=\"962\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">5、用实力回击霍顿，孙杨世锦赛400自决赛夺冠。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（最后50米优势达到2秒以上，霍顿该为自己的言行羞愧了。）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><br></p>\n<hr style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015102MUh9D4.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.15162907268170425\" data-w=\"798\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1、人民日报海外版：19个省区市公布经济半年报，重庆增速居首。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（15个省（区、市）的GDP增速均明显高于全国水平，贵州和重庆更是突破了10%，重庆以10.5%的增速居于首位。）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2、碧桂园首次跻身财富世界500强，或成首家年销售金额超5000亿元房企。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（仅今年上半年，碧桂园便完成销售金额2889.1亿元，销售面积3226万平方米，两项核心指标均位居行业第一，是目前全球销售规模最大的房地产开发企业。）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3、贾跃亭旗下价值160亿元乐视网股票被冻结：私募申请财产保全。</span></strong></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015102ZrcXz9.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7078125\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4、B站董事长回应影视剧下架：完全是自我审查，还要持续一两月。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（如果是通过审查的内容会陆续上线，没有通过的，就永远不会恢复了。）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">5、美媒称，中国正在进行一场大胆的经济实验。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（如何系统、快速地终结了纸币和硬币的使用。）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><br></p>\n<hr style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/201707270151028RXBjr.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.15194805194805194\" data-w=\"770\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1、新华社：高铁、支付宝、共享单车和网购被称作中国“新四大发明”。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（曾以古代“四大发明”推动世界进步的中国，正再次以科技创新向世界展示自己的发展理念。）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2、\"共享睡眠舱\"被叫停，警方:提供住宿必须有许可证。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（警方调查发现，易被违法犯罪人员利用，藏身落脚；发生火灾后无法及时扑灭逃生，存在治安和消防隐患。）</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3、“怀旧小轮”夏日启航，香港打造旅游新景点。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（其中上海迪士尼、广州长隆度假区、鼓浪屿、黄山、秦始皇陵兵马俑、张家界、圆明园、中华恐龙园、天门山玻璃栈道、西溪湿地进入热门景区排行榜前十。）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4、海南美兰机场开设女性旅客安检专用通道。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">(首设安检女子班组，配备9名女性安检员开展服务工作。)</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015102KanHbN.jpg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><br></p>\n<hr style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015103sXW6AM.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.16389244558258642\" data-w=\"781\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1、中国发现新型发电材料：未来或可用衣物的弯折给手机充电。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（主要是通过衣服受挤压或拉伸时可以产生电。）</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015103c8ptnY.jpg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2、印度火炮试验失败，都是中国零件的锅？</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（厂家将从中国河南采购的产品伪造检验报告说成德国货。）</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015103T6FXxW.jpg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7490909090909091\" data-w=\"550\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3、阿里百度腾讯京东800亿元投资联通?官方回应。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;  color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;\">（与潜在投资者的谈判工作仍在进行中，但不排除可能。）</span></p>\n<p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"http://wechats.zhonghuilv.net/uploads/article/2017-07-27/20170727015103E7nTYO.jpg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60625\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:auto;max-width:100%;\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong style=\"letter-s